Text: The Customer Service Representative sends a Mortgage offer to the customer and waits for a reply.
If the customer calls or writes back declining the mortgage, the case details are updated and the work is then archived prior to cancellation.
Constraints extracted: [PRECEDENCE(A=the customer calls or writes back declining the mortgage , B=update case detail), PRECEDENCE(A=the customer calls or writes back declining the mortgage , B=archive work)]

Text: If the customer sends back the completed offer documents and attaches all prerequisite documents then the case is moved to administration for completion.
Constraints extracted: [EXISTENCE(A=the customer sends back the completed offer documents and attaches all prerequisite documents then )]

Text: If all pre-requisite documents are not provided a message is generated to the customer requesting outstanding documents.
Constraints extracted: [PRECEDENCE(A=all pre-requisite documents are not provided , B=generate message)]

Text: If no answer is received after 2 weeks, the case details are updated prior to archive and cancellation.
Constraints extracted: [PRECEDENCE(A=no answer is received after 2 weeks , B=update case detail)]
